snippet.title: Temple Run: Legends - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Temple Run: Legends, the first level-based runner within the Temple Run family and features all-new gameplay modes, challenges, and rewards!

Run, swim, and hop on crocodile heads to achieve a 3-star rating on hundreds of levels.
Experience the different climates, inhabitants and challenges of this new land as you run from level to level with a wide cast of characters!

Only on Apple Arcade: https://apple.co/4d6hX9B

Follow Temple Run: Legends for more:
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61563367560087/
X (Twitter) - https://x.com/TempleRunLegend/
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/templerun_legends/
